name: Jumpy Skating in Beverly Hill
description:
** BE CAREFUL: ONLY FOR PRO GAMER ***

Are you ready for the ultimate challenge?
The new Jumpy Skating in Beverly Hill is now on your iPhone, iPod and iPad!

Download this game now!
